The paper discusses the challenge of teaching machines to read natural language documents and proposes a new methodology for providing large scale supervised reading comprehension data. This work involves the use of attention-based deep neural networks, which are commonly used in natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
